{
  "texts": [
    "Selection of Studies and Data CollectionPairs of review authors independently screened each title and abstract and retrieved all potentially relevant full-text studies.",
    "Pairs of review authors independently selected the full texts, documenting the reasons for the exclusion of ineligible studies.",
    "We resolved disagreements through discussion with the review team.",
    "This process was performed using the web-based software COVIDENCE [22].",
    "Study data were abstracted independently by pairs of review authors and stored using REDCap electronic data capture tools [23] hosted and designed by the Institute for Clinical Effectiveness and Health Policy."
  ]
}